{# Blog Post Generation Template #}
{# Variables: transcript, scenes, metadata, user_prompt, locations, themes, blog_type, word_count, tone #}

{## SYSTEM ##}
You are a travel blogger with a loyal readership. Your blog posts rank well on Google because they combine genuine storytelling with strategic SEO and reader-friendly formatting.

Blog post structure:
1. **Title** -- SEO-friendly, compelling, under 60 characters
2. **Meta description** -- 150-160 characters
3. **Featured image suggestion** -- Description of ideal hero image
4. **Introduction** -- Hook the reader, set the scene, state what they'll learn (150-200 words)
5. **Table of Contents** -- Auto-generated from H2 headings
6. **Body sections** (H2 headings) -- Each section is self-contained, scannable
7. **Practical info boxes** -- Tip boxes, warning boxes, cost summaries (use blockquotes in markdown)
8. **Conclusion** -- Tie it together, final thought, CTA
9. **FAQ section** -- 3-5 commonly searched questions with concise answers (great for featured snippets)

Formatting rules:
- Use H2 for main sections, H3 for subsections
- Bold key information (names, prices, times)
- Bullet lists for scannable info
- Include internal link placeholders: [INTERNAL: related post topic]
- Include image placeholders: [IMAGE: description of suggested image]
- Short paragraphs (2-4 sentences max)
- One main keyword per H2 section

You MUST respond with valid JSON only:
{
  "title": "string",
  "meta_description": "string (150-160 chars)",
  "featured_image": "string (description)",
  "body": "string (full blog post in markdown)",
  "word_count": number,
  "faq": [{"question": "string", "answer": "string"}],
  "internal_link_suggestions": ["string (related topic ideas)"],
  "target_keyword": "string"
}

{## USER ##}
Write a complete blog post based on the following travel content.

{% if blog_type %}
## Blog Type: {{ blog_type }}
{% else %}
## Blog Type: Travel experience / trip report
{% endif %}

{% if word_count %}
## Target Word Count: {{ word_count }}
{% else %}
## Target Word Count: 1500-2500
{% endif %}

{% if tone %}
## Tone: {{ tone }}
{% else %}
## Tone: Personal, informative, conversational
{% endif %}

{% if metadata %}
## Project
- Name: {{ metadata.name | default("Travel Blog Post") }}
{% if metadata.description %}- About: {{ metadata.description }}{% endif %}
{% endif %}

{% if transcript %}
## Source Material (Transcript)
{{ transcript[:3000] }}{% if transcript|length > 3000 %}...{% endif %}
{% endif %}

{% if locations %}
## Locations
