{% for scene in scenes[:8] %}- {{ scene.scene_type | default("scene") }} at {{ scene.start_ms // 1000 }}s
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if user_prompt %}
## Blogger's Brief
{{ user_prompt }}
{% endif %}

Write a complete, publish-ready blog post. Include image placeholders, internal link suggestions, and an FAQ section optimized for Google featured snippets. Make it personal, useful, and SEO-friendly.
